			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第八条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方有义务在注册、</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">信息认证</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">时提供完整、真实、准确的信息及相关注册及</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">认证</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">资料，保证该信息及资料内容的持续完整性、真实性、有效性及合法性，并同意甲方通过必要方式对其身份和资质进行审核。乙方信息及相关资料发生变更时，乙方有义务及时在普托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">e</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">享更新有关注册及</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">认证</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">资料。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第九条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">因乙方的信息或其他注册资料不完整、不真实、不准确、失效或违法而导致</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">无法提供服务或提供服务时发生任何错误，乙方不得将此作为取消交易、拒绝付款的理由，由此产生的全部法律后果由乙方承担，因此给甲方或其他第三方造成损失的，乙方应予以赔偿。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方通过普托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">e</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">享所在网站上注册为企业</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">以后，有权使用自己的登录名称及密码登录普托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">e</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">享。乙方应妥善保管自己的登录名称及密码，避免以不安全的方式或在不安全的环境下使用密码，切勿将密码以任何形式透露给任何他人，或以易被他人发现、获得、盗用的方式保管。乙方应对使用其登录名称以及密码而从事的一切交易或非交易行为承担法律责任。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十一条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方办理</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">业务应直接登录普托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">e</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">享的官方网站，而不应通过未经</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">认可的邮件或其他网站提供的链接登录。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十二条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方承诺其在使用</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">服务时的所有行为遵守国家法律、法规以及甲方相关规则并符合社会公共利益或公共道德。乙方应对其在普托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">e</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">享或</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">服务中传输、发送、发布的全部信息内容负全部责任。因乙方在普托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">e</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">享或</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">服务中传输、发送、发布的信息内容而导致甲方或其他第三方任何直接或间接损失的，该乙方应承担全部责任，并应赔偿甲方或第三方因此遭受的全部损失。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十三条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">在使用本服务时，若乙方或乙方的交易对手未遵从本服务条款或网站说明、交易页面中之操作提示、规则，则甲方有权拒绝为乙方与交易对方提供相关服务，且甲方不承担损害赔偿责任。因乙方的原因导致甲方或第三方损失的，甲方有权向乙方追索赔偿，乙方应当承担甲方因追索而支出的合理费用。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十四条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">因乙方自身的原因导致的任何损失由乙方自行承担，原因包括但不限于：乙方不按照交易提示操作，乙方未及时进行交易操作，乙方发送的交易指令错误或不完整。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十五条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">为方便乙方使用甲方及甲方关联公司或其他组织的服务，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">乙方对自身信息的使用作出如下授权：</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">本人授权</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普拉托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">，除法律另有规定之外，将本人提供给</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普拉托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">的信息、享受</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">服务产生的信息（包括本协议签署之前提供和产生的信息）以及</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普拉托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">根据本条约定查询、收集的信息，用于</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普拉托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">及其因服务必要委托的合作伙伴为本人提供服务、推荐产品、开展市场调查与信息数据分析。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">本人授权</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普拉托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">，除法律另有规定之外，基于为本人提供更优质服务和产品的目的，向</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普拉托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">因服务必要开展合作的伙伴提供、查询、收集本人的信息。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">为确保本人信息的安全，</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普拉托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">及其合作伙伴对上述信息负有保密义务，并采取各种措施保证信息安全。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">本条款自本协议签署时生效，具有独立法律效力，不受合同成立与否及效力状态变化的影响。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">本条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">款</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">所称</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">“普拉托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">”是指</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">深圳市普拉托科技</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">有限公司及其直接或间接控股的公司</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">。</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">如乙方不同意上述授权条款的部分或全部，可〔致电客服热线〕取消或变更授权。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十六条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方对于其发布在甲方所在网站的各类信息（但不包括乙方的身份信息）以及其派生的知识产权等，均授予甲方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普拉托</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">独家的、全球通用的、永久的、免费的许可使用权，甲方有权对之以电子或书面等方式进行使用、复制、发行、修订、改写、发布、翻译、分发、执行和展示或制作其派生作品。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十七条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方不得使用与</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">正常业务无关的任何软硬件装置，用于干预或试图干预</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">的正常运作或正在</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">进行的任何交易。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十八条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方不得对</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">上的任何资料作商业性利用，包括但不限于在未经甲方授权的情况下，复制在平台上展示的任何资料并用于商业用途。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第十九条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方在使用本服务过程中，本协议内容、网页上出现的关于交易操作的提示说明或甲方发送给乙方的信息（通过向乙方预留手机发送短信</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">、</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">通过电话语音形式发送</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">或通过向乙方预留电子邮箱发送邮件</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">）内容是乙方使用本服务的相关规则的组成部分，乙方使用本服务即表示乙方同意接受该相关规则。乙方了解并同意甲方有权单方修改本服务的相关规则，乙方同意并遵照甲方的相关服务规则是乙方使用本服务的前提。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方应对其在注册</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">和接受甲方的</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">服务过程中设置、发布的所有信息内容负全部责任，如甲方因此遭受损失的，甲方有权向乙方追偿。乙方在注册</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">和接受</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">服务过程中设置、传输、发送、发布的信息不得包含以下内容：</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">（1）反对宪法所确定的基本原则和制度；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">（2）危害国家安全，泄露国家秘密，颠覆国家政权，破坏国家统一；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">（3）损害国家荣誉和利益；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">（4）煽动民族仇恨、民族歧视，破坏民族团结；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">（5）破坏国家宗教政策，宣扬邪教和封建迷信；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">（6）散布谣言，扰乱社会秩序，破坏社会稳定；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">（7）散布淫秽、色情、赌博、暴力、凶杀、恐怖或者教唆犯罪；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">（8）侮辱或者诽谤他人，侵害他人合法权益；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">（9）侵犯他人著作权、商标权等知识产权或合法权利；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">（10）以虚构或歪曲事实的方式评价商品或商户；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">（11）含有法律、行政法规禁止的其他内容。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">甲方有权审查乙方的注册资料及信息发布情况，如发现存在违反法律、本协议和业务管理规则的情形，有权采取要求乙方说明情况、删除信息、注销</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">资格等必要措施，乙方应当予以配合。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:center; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第四章 甲方的主要权利和义务</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">一</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">甲方应在现有条件下提高服务质量，确保为</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">提供的服务顺利进行。</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">如因不可抗力或甲方控制范围外的原因造成的服务中断或其他缺陷（包括但不限于自然灾害、社会事件、硬件故障以及因网站所具有的特殊性质而产生的包括黑客攻击、电信部门技术调整导致的影响、政府管制而造成的暂时性关闭在内的任何影响网络正常运营的因素），甲方不承担任何责任，但将尽力减少因此而给</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">造成的损失和影响。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">任何由于甲方合理控制范围以外的原因而产生的交易或服务系统问题，造成资料、</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">交易</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">等信息传输或储存上的错误，导致资料泄露、丢失、被盗用或被篡改等，致使甲方平台响应延迟或未能履约的，甲方不承担对此可能造成的任何责任。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">二</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">甲方有权依据其内部业务规定及商业判断独立决定是否同意乙方所申请事项（包括但不限于</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">资格</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">申请、</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">租赁</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">申请等）。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">三</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方的登录名、密码遭到未经授权的使用或发生其他任何安全问题时，乙方应立即通知甲方。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">四</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">甲方对自身发布的公告信息真实性负责。</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">及</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户信息、</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">及</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户的产品/服务信息（包括但不限于公司名称、联系人及联络信息，产品/服务的描述和说明，相关图片等）均由乙方提供，乙方依法应对其提供的任何信息承担全部责任。</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">甲方对此等信息的准确性、完整性、合法性或真实性均不承担任何责任。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">五</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">甲方对服务中涉及的乙方资料负有保密义务，但发生下述情况的除外：</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">（1）本协议另有约定或事先获得乙方的明确授权或应允；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">（2）根据有关的法律法规要求；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">（3）按照相关政府主管部门或司法机关按法定程序的要求；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">（4）为维护社会公众的利益；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">（5）披露前已为公众所知悉；</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">（6）为维护甲方的合法权益。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">六</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">对于乙方在甲方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">上的不当行为（包括但不限于违反</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">所做承诺或约定义务、违反</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">规则等）或其它任何甲方认为应当终止服务的情况，甲方有权采取删除或屏蔽乙方发布的信息、限制或终止全部或部分服务、解除协议、列入黑名单、网站公示等一项或多项处理措施，并保留追究其法律责任的权利。甲方在有证据证明乙方或具体交易事项存在违法违规或违反本协议等问题时，有权根据不同情况选择做出给予乙方包括但不限于警告、公示、限权、终止服务等不同程度的处罚，并保留追究其相关法律责任的权利。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">七</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">甲方有权对乙方的账户资料及交易行为进行查阅，发现账户资料或交易行为违反本协议约定的，均有权向乙方发出询问的通知，并有权根据具体情况要求乙方改正或依据本协议规定采取相应措施。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第二十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">八</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">甲方有权自主排列乙方在页面的展示位置。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">二十九</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">仅作为乙方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">开立设备账户，出租、承租、购买、转让托盘等相关服务的平台。乙方应自行判断交易商品或服务的质量、安全，商品或服务信</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">息的真实性、合法性、准确性，以及交易各方履行其交易合同的能力。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三十条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">对交易各方发生的争议，甲方有权依据争议任何一方的要求向相关单位提交系统记录作为证据。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">一</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方同意甲方在乙方的计算机上设定或取用与</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">交易相关的有关信息。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">二</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">乙方同意，甲方有权根据业务需要将本协议项下的全部或部分权利义务转让给其关联公司，发生此种情况时甲方仅需提前以网站公告的形式通知乙方即可。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">三</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">其他具体约定参阅</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">的相关规则。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:center; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:center; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第五章 收费</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">四</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">乙方因交易或使用</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">普托e 享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">而发生的所有应纳税赋以及费用全部由乙方自行承担。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">五</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">甲方有权向乙方收取相关服务费用。甲方拥有制订及调整服务费用的权利，具体服务费用标准及收取规则将以网站公示的方式进行公告，不再单独通知乙方。自公告施行之日公告内容构成对甲方与</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">间协议约定的有效修改和补充。如果乙方不同意接受甲方有关公告的内容，应当立即停止使用该等服务费用相关的甲方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">服务。乙方续使用与该等服务费用相关的甲方</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">服务的，即视为乙方接受甲方公告的服务费用标准及收取规则。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:center; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:center; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第六章 责任范围及责任限制</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">六</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">甲方仅负责按当时现状和当时可得到的状态向乙方提供</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">服务。除非甲方另行以书面方式明确无误的作出承诺，否则甲方对</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">服务不作任何明示或暗示的保证，包括但不限于</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">服务的适用性、没有错误或疏漏、持续性、准确性、可靠性、适用于某一特定用途；甲方也不对</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">服务所涉及的技术及信息的有效性、准确性、正确性、可靠性、质量、稳定、完整和及时性作出任何承诺和保证。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">七</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">甲方无法控制交易所涉及的产品/服务的质量、安全或合法性，商贸信息的真实性或准确性，以及交易各方履行其在贸易协议中各项义务的能力。乙方应自行谨慎判断确定相关产品/服务或信息的真实性、合法性和有效性，并自行承担因此产生的责任与损失。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">第三十</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">八</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">条</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">除非甲方明确予以承诺，甲方不对乙方与其他</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">之间的交易提供任何形式的保证，不介入</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">用户</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">通过</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">进行交易而产生的纠纷，因通过</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">普托e享</span><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; font-weight:bold; text-transform:none">进行交易产生的风险和损失由乙方自行承担。</span></p>
			<p style="line-height:18pt; margin:0pt; text-align:justify; text-indent:24pt"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑; font-size:10.5pt; font-style:normal; text-transform:none">&#xa0;</span></p>
